{"tid":1834416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【化解死亡之吻】葉劉直踩小店幫襯$94漢堡 呼籲勿做黃色經濟圈 老闆：立刻將錢捐畀立場新聞","createTime":"2020-01-22T11:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T21:57:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4772eaaef32e9c63c947b7c9f36244e53ec0956c","tid":1834416,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"抗暴之戰中，不少名人都被視為死亡之吻，最有名莫過於新民黨主席葉劉淑儀，西營盤小菜館加記被她光顧及出Post後，曾傳言老闆要求刪Post。<br />\n<br />\n1月22日的午飯時間，銅鑼灣平民牛扒店Top Blade就遇上這死亡之吻！負責人Edgar笑說當時情況：「她當時走進餐廳，點了牛油果煎蛋漢堡包，突然直衝入廚房，問我們有沒有登記做飲食界選民，我答有登記後，她再問我商業登記在哪兒。」<br />\n<br />\n原來葉太是幫同事勸餐廳持牌人登記做選民。不過Top Blade負責人Edgar立刻表明黃店立場，並向葉太表示多謝光顧黃店：「葉太明顯打咗個突，然後說無問題，但就勸我們不要暴力，最好不要搞黃色經濟，但我告訴她不是我們發起的。」最後葉太沒有吃所點的漢堡，並打包離去。<br />\n<br />\nEdgar笑說當時葉太笑容滿面，很有禮貌，但廚房遇見葉太的情況太超現實，差點切到手。老闆還大方捐出葉太光顧的$94予立場新聞，希望同路人能夠多多支持。<br />\n<br />\nTop Blade Steak Lab<br />\n地址：銅鑼灣希慎道2-4號地舖<br />\n電話：2657 8210<br />\n營業時間：12nn-10pm<br />\n詳情： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NP8rjy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NP8rjy&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=a7c85722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NP8rjy</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200122/large/1579679359_9e1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200122%2Flarge%2F1579679359_9e1f.jpg&h=facd007c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20200122/HI6MB6KSYCLD6XHFEACYGCKVLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200122%2FHI6MB6KSYCLD6XHFEACYGCKVLI%2F&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=5b6d3e03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2FETW%2F20200122%2FHI6MB6KSYCLD6XHFEACYGCKVLI%2F&h=be82617d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/ETW/20200122/HI6MB6KSYCLD6XHFEACYGCKVLI/</a>"},{"pid":"64cc338ed9167bf90fffe09196c8615f8557c1fd","tid":1834416,"uid":303805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230f9fff1c4f33e4367ed5e03416ef68af4ecd32","tid":1834416,"uid":224882,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />型"},{"pid":"dd78873bd614faf74c7f50ae9f5a9e171b55b274","tid":1834416,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"top blade早期已黃， 好似係"},{"pid":"6def09877db70dbc27bc7eb815637956da4fc038","tid":1834416,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"佢都和你eat <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728f505d71a21118db3f7d4907d91bf1c2dc64fa","tid":1834416,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T12:11:36.000Z","msg":"幫襯得黃店就係自己人<br />\n<br />\n以後行會靠你收風"},{"pid":"35312898f19fd9e458db63a204130f12dc12a5e4","tid":1834416,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64cc338ed9167bf90fffe09196c8615f8557c1fd","tid":1834416,"uid":303805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:17:24.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T21:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}